{"tid":1851481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叫人唔好買曬啲口罩係錯誤，見到有就盡量買先可以幫到同路人，減少益藍絲嘅機會","createTime":"2020-01-30T05:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T12:01:10.000Z","uid":61282,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b610963308de81ef48b1f86a5b4f2cf61177ca4","tid":1851481,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:04:15.000Z","msg":"原文link: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/121622707864693/posts/3299833803376885/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F121622707864693%2Fposts%2F3299833803376885%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=d62bb4ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/121622707864693/posts/3299833803376885/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n唉，本來真係無興趣教黃絲啲垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n乜嘢叫大家唔好買曬啲口罩？上網買除外？！<br />\n<br />\n黃絲大愛左膠，不如等我地講白啲。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢，你留番啲貨係門市，只係會被藍絲買到，又或講得衰啲，啲貨可能由後門唔知走咗去邊，結果都係做炒貨。<br />\n<br />\n即係話，你留番係門市根本好大機會幫唔到基層或有需要嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n若果你仲買到或有地方買到，請：<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊有貨就盡買，唔該＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊有貨就盡買，唔該＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊有貨就盡買，唔該＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n你咁想幫基層，又或者有需要嘅人，有好多方法，搵一搵區議員已經可以幫到手。再唔係上網開個post，我地幫你免費轉發，又有咩問題。最少啲罩係你手，你話要講「光復香港，時代革命」先拎得都無問題，咁樣確保你幫到同路人呀最少。<br />\n<br />\n下次唔該唔好人傳你又傳，用個腦諗一諗成件事幾咁柒。就算留番啲貨係間黃店門市，黃店都好難話唔俾藍絲阿伯排廿次、又或有有廿萬個藍絲阿伯買曬啲貨去囤。<br />\n<br />\n係呢場仗打緊，唔好再做大愛撚。要大愛，都大愛得醒少少好無？唔好到時身邊有朋友無罩用，你先黎覺得自己on99。<br />\n<br />\n利申：張圖入面篇文on9嘅地方好多身邊朋友都諗到，唔係得我地懶醒諗到，我地忍唔住先係度爆，真係忍唔到先咁夜係度講⋯<br />\n<br />\n㩒下： <a href=\"http://winandmac.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwinandmac.com&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=b0504015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">winandmac.com</a>"},{"pid":"af3a3c8c37c5f08307055163ccd31e7cc2ef9838","tid":1851481,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"求求大家<br />\n明白肺炎好恐怖<br />\n貨源都好緊張<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好放棄國際戰線<br />\n好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></span><br />\n全部英美議員講野唔過千<br />\n<br />\n已經連續三日都係咁<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=32bd0f7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"862184d5fcec1f65eac760084eb20af7c5009cfe","tid":1851481,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護手足 點可以因為一場本可以封關避免嘅病毒而賭上生命<br />\n我地仲未光復到香港啊..<br />\nbtw p牌求推一推... <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥 借刀殺人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850782</a>"},{"pid":"8f995378252557958187395bd2d7ac93ce9cb57a","tid":1851481,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a25d16185cec9a9e1a94d284fec60429078c4bcb","tid":1851481,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"放棄買口罩糧食=放棄掌握資源=無執政意志=舊民主派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851652</a>"},{"pid":"ba6690c261a485a3491c12ddded05738a1955288","tid":1851481,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"好多藍絲仔女係黃"},{"pid":"c30cf6575ce8ba98e1d00bb8872b358fbbd27384","tid":1851481,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"口罩 同 關愛座 一樣：<br />\n<br />\n先擁有(ownership)<br />\n後轉贈(donate)"},{"pid":"96df5c5e0e8913703ae0771a405e5cad61cb93f6","tid":1851481,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:27:50.000Z","msg":"有貨=有權揀客"},{"pid":"12dc474049e82240c7b064149b627a08c8624c59","tid":1851481,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"睇住逼到班藍屍狗急跳牆<br />\n你知佢地唔會鬧政府<br />\n話唔定去黃絲屋企爆格<br />\n警甴又唔會捉"},{"pid":"ca1b26d293dd72ff03eedb5c777bd16f4f7312fa","tid":1851481,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:37:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港政府口罩存倉地點：<br />\n(1) 柴灣創富道11號政府物料營運中心<br />\n(2) 葵涌冠華鏡廠第三工業大廈</span>"},{"pid":"9a20cda97de0110451c732984a14360ab36a62d1","tid":1851481,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dc85230d70f354d5b9234684715590788784b4","tid":1851481,"uid":306879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n買家自律根本天方夜譚<br />\n緊急時勢應該要賣家嚴格限購<br />\n就算唔用實名制, 會員證識用喇掛"}]}